SimulatorView
Copyright 2026 Yuta Ooka (https://github.com/subdiox)

This product includes software developed at tddworks (https://github.com/tddworks/baguette).
The CoreSimulator + SimulatorKit runtime bridge (`CoreSimulatorRuntime`, `SimDeviceResolver`)
and the IOSurface framebuffer streaming logic (`SimulatorFramebuffer`) are derived from
baguette's `Sources/Baguette/Infrastructure/Simulator/CoreSimulators.swift` and
`Sources/Baguette/Infrastructure/Screen/SimulatorKitScreen.swift`, both Apache 2.0 licensed.

Modifications:
- Repackaged as a standalone library with a public AppKit/SwiftUI surface.
- Removed CLI-specific scaffolding (logging, error reporting via stderr, host-side
  domain types, gesture registry, HTTP server integration).
- Switched concurrency model to Swift 6 actors / @MainActor isolation; eliminated
  @unchecked Sendable and nonisolated(unsafe) static state.
